reviewText: I rated this dvd a 5 because, I saw this movie when I was a young adult. I like this movie because, they restored it back to the way is was suppose too be. Any kung- Fu fan or collector, if they have this move on vhs or dvd. I would tell them to get this one, because it's be digitally remastered.
Just thought I'd let everyone know, I've seen this movie countless times at Walmarts allover MN for only $1. Save yourself some money if you really want to get this movie, get it there.

I have to give this movie a 4 star because of all the times i seen it. I literally watch this movie 100 times when i was 14, becuase i would watch it while i worked out. It was the first movie i got when i first got into martial arts and bruce lee. Yeah its a pretty cool movie, i brought it a walmart for a dollar.
